#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.homepage
msgid "&amp;nbsp;<br/>"
msgstr "&amp;nbsp;<br/>"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.homepage
msgid ""
"&amp;nbsp;For larger projects, we offer comprehensive services that include "
"<b>on-site installation</b> and meticulous project management, ensuring a "
"smooth and successful completion from start to finish."
msgstr ""
"&amp;nbsp;Untuk project lebih besar, kami menawarkan layanan-layanan "
"komprehensif termasuk <b>penginstalan di-tempat</b> dan manajemen project "
"rinci, memastikan penyelesaian yang mulus dan lengkap dari awal sampai akhir."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.homepage
msgid ""
"&amp;nbsp;Our expertise extends across diverse industries. We provide custom "
"metal fabrication services for both <b>individuals</b> and <b>businesses</b> "
"in sectors like <b>agriculture</b>, <b>automotive</b>, and "
"<b>pharmaceuticals</b>, ensuring we meet the unique demands of each project."
msgstr ""
"&amp;nbsp;Keahlian kami sampai ke beragam industri-industri. Kami "
"menyediakan layanan pembuatan logam kustom untuk <b>individu</b> dan "
"<b>bisnis </b>di sektor-sektor seperti <b>agrikultur</b>, <b>otomotif</b>, "
"dan <b>farmasi</b>, memastikan kami memenuhi tuntutan unik dari setiap "
"project."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.homepage
msgid ""
"<a class=\"btn btn-secondary mb-2 o_translate_inline\" href=\"/"
"contactus\">Get your project started</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a class=\"btn btn-secondary mb-2 o_translate_inline\" href=\"/"
"contactus\">Mulai project Anda</a>"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Accounting:</b> Automatically log payments, close sessions, and generate "
"tax reports."
msgstr ""
"<b>Akuntansi:</b> Otomatis rekam pembayaran, tutup sesi, dan buat laporan "
"pajak."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Adjust the expected arrival date</b> as needed."
msgstr "<b>Sesuaikan tanggal kedatangan yang diharapkan</b> sesuai kebutuhan."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Buy:</b> Select this if the product is purchased from a vendor."
msgstr "<b>Beli:</b> Pilih ini bila produk dibeli dari vendor."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Combine RFQs:</b> If you have multiple requests for quotation (RFQs) from "
"the same vendor, you can group them into a single order."
msgstr ""
"<b>Gabungkan RFQ:</b> Jika ada beberapa permintaan penawaran (RFQ) dari "
"vendor yang sama, Anda dapat menggabungkannya menjadi satu pesanan."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Create a purchase order</b> and add the products and services you need."
msgstr ""
"<b>Buat purchase order</b> dan tambahkan produk serta layanan yang "
"diperlukan."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Field Service:</b> Plan and monitor on-site installations."
msgstr "<b>Layanan Lapangan:</b> Rencanakan dan pantau pemasangan di lokasi."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Inventory Tracking:</b> In this database, we've decided not to track "
"products using a Warehouse Management System, even though Odoo offers this "
"feature. While inventory tracking improves stock accuracy and forecasting, "
"it also requires more administrative tasks to ensure all operations are "
"validated on time. If you wish to implement inventory tracking, you can find "
"more information in the official documentation."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pelacakan Inventaris:</b> Di database ini, kami memutuskan untuk tidak "
"melacak produk menggunakan Sistem Manajemen Gudang, meskipun Odoo menawarkan "
"fitur ini. Meskipun pelacakan inventaris meningkatkan akurasi stok dan "
"prakiraan, hal ini juga memerlukan lebih banyak tugas administratif untuk "
"memastikan semua operasi bisa diverifikasi tepat waktu. Jika Anda ingin "
"menerapkan pelacakan inventaris, informasi lebih lanjut dapat diakses di "
"dokumentasi resmi."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Inventory:</b> Track and manage all your products within a custom-"
"designed warehouse."
msgstr ""
"<b>Inventaris:</b> Lacak dan kelola semua produk di gudang yang dirancang "
"khusus."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Manufacture:</b> Choose this if the product is made in-house."
msgstr "<b>Manufaktur:</b> Pilih ini jika produk diproduksi secara internal."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Open the Manufacturing Order</b> and add the necessary components."
msgstr "<b>Buka Manufacturing Order</b> dan tambahkan komponen yang diperlukan."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Production Guidance:</b> If you have employees on the shop floor who need "
"guidance on manufacturing processes, consider exploring the <b>Work Order</"
"b> feature and <b>Shopfloor</b> application. They are designed to provide "
"operational support and instructions for your team. See documentation about "
"it if you want to implement."
msgstr ""
"<b>Panduan Produksi:</b> Jika ada karyawan di area produksi yang memerlukan "
"panduan mengenai proses produksi, coba fitur <b>SPK</b> (Surat Perintah "
"Kerja) dan aplikasi <b>Shopfloor</b>. Keduanya dirancang untuk memberikan "
"dukungan operasional dan instruksi bagi tim. Lihat dokumentasinya jika Anda "
"ingin mengimplementasikannya."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Setting up the Purchase App</b>"
msgstr "<b>Menyiapkan Aplikasi Purchase</b>"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate the order</b> to confirm it."
msgstr "<b>Validasi pesanan</b> untuk mengonfirmasinya."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>CRM &amp; Sales App</b>:</font> Manage all "
"product and service charges for your clients, creating detailed quotations "
"for bespoke items."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi CRM &amp; Sales</b>:</font> "
"Kelola semua biaya produk dan layanan untuk klien Anda, serta buat penawaran "
"harga yang mendetail untuk barang-barang khusus."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Inventory App</b>:</font> Keep strict "
"control over your raw metals, hardware, and finished components across your "
"warehouse and production floor."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi Inventaris</b>:</font> Kontrol "
"ketat persediaan logam mentah, perangkat keras, dan komponen jadi di seluruh "
"gudang dan area produksi Anda."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Invoicing App</b>:</font> Keep track of "
"all your invoices, handling progress billing for long-term projects or "
"standard invoicing for direct sales."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi Faktur</b>:</font> Lacak semua "
"faktur, mulai dari penagihan bertahap untuk proyek jangka panjang hingga "
"penagihan standar untuk sales langsung."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Manufacturing App</b>:</font> Handle the "
"creation of all your products, managing bills of materials (BoMs) and work "
"centers for everything from cutting to welding."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi Manufaktur</b>:</font> Kelola "
"pembuatan semua produk, termasuk bill of material (BoM) dan pusat kerja "
"untuk semua proses, mulai dari pemotongan hingga pengelasan."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Project App</b>:</font> Manage complex "
"fabrication projects that involve multiple production stages and "
"installation phases efficiently."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi Project</b>:</font> Kelola proyek "
"fabrikasi kompleks yang melibatkan berbagai tahap produksi dan fase "
"pemasangan secara efisien."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Purchase App</b>:</font> Ensure accurate "
"inventory replenishment for raw materials and track <b>subcontracting "
"services</b> for specialized treatments like galvanizing."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi Purchase</b>:</font> Pastikan "
"inventaris bahan baku selalu akurat dan lacak <b>layanan subkontrak</b> "
"untuk prosedur khusus seperti galvanisasi."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Website App</b>:</font> Act as a virtual "
"showroom to display your past projects and specialized capabilities, serving "
"as a powerful tool for generating new leads."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Aplikasi Website</b>:</font> Menjadi "
"pameran virtual untuk menampilkan proyek-proyek lampau dan keahlian khusus "
"Anda, berperan sebagai alat ampuh untuk menghasilkan prospek baru."

