#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For all other scenarios, you can create and manage purchase orders directly "
"in the <b>Purchase</b> app. The main dashboard provides a clear overview of "
"all your orders."
msgstr ""
"Untuk skenario lainnya, Anda dapat membuat dan mengelola purchase order "
"langsung di aplikasi <b>Purchase</b>. Dashboard utama menyajikan gambaran "
"yang jelas mengenai semua pesanan Anda."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For any components you need to generate a <b>sub-assembly</b> or a "
"<b>purchase order</b>, make sure the <b>\"Replenish on Order\"</b> route is "
"set. Other items can be added to the BOM for informational or cost-"
"calculation purposes only."
msgstr ""
"Untuk komponen apa pun yang memerlukan <b>sub-rakitan</b> atau <b>purchase "
"order</b>, pastikan rute <b>Replenish on Order</b> telah ditetapkan. Item "
"lain dapat ditambahkan ke BOM hanya untuk tujuan informasi atau perhitungan "
"biaya."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For complex projects, add the \"<strong>Project Management</strong>\" "
"service to track the quotation within a dedicated project."
msgstr ""
"Untuk proyek yang kompleks, tambahkan layanan \"<strong>Project Management</"
"strong>\" untuk melacak penawaran harga dalam proyek khusus."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For each product you want to <strong>produce, create a BIll Of Material</"
"strong> and leave it empty. This way you will always manually add the needed "
"components after the Sales Order is created."
msgstr ""
"Untuk setiap produk yang ingin <strong>diproduksi, buatlah Bill of Material</"
"strong> dan kosongkan. Dengan cara ini, Anda akan selalu menambahkan "
"komponen yang diperlukan secara manual setelah Sales Order dibuat."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For each product you want to <strong>purchase, add a vendor</strong> in the "
"purchase tab (mandatory to have at least one)"
msgstr ""
"Untuk setiap produk yang ingin Anda <strong>beli, tambahkan vendor</strong> "
"di tab pembelian (wajib ada minimal satu)"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For effective planning and follow-up, simply use the pre-set filters "
"available in the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Untuk perencanaan dan follow-up yang efektif, cukup gunakan filter bawaan "
"yang tersedia di kolom pencarian."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For other cases, or for manual follow-up, open the <b>Manufacturing Order "
"app</b>. The main dashboard <span style=\"width: 0px;\" class=\"oe-"
"tabs\">\t</span>​​provides a clear overview of all outstanding production "
"orders."
msgstr ""
"Untuk kasus lain, atau untuk follow-up manual, buka <b>aplikasi "
"Manufacturing Order</b>. Dashboard utama <span style=\"width: 0px;\" "
"class=\"oe-tabs\">\t</span>​​​​menyajikan gambaran umum yang jelas mengenai "
"semua order produksi yang masih tertunda."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <b>Inventory App</b>, you can adapt and validate all receipts or "
"deliveries."
msgstr ""
"Dari <b>Aplikasi Inventaris</b>, Anda dapat menyesuaikan dan memvalidasi "
"semua resi atau pengiriman."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.footer
msgid "Get in touch"
msgstr "Get in touch"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.footer
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Beranda"

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If a product is configured with \"Replenish on Order\" and \"Buy\" routes, a "
"purchase order is automatically generated from a sales or manufacturing "
"order. After confirming the sales or manufacturing order, a smart button "
"will appear, redirecting you to a new <b>Request for Quotation (RFQ)</b>. "
"You can make any necessary changes before confirming it."
msgstr ""
"Jika suatu produk dikonfigurasi dengan rute \"Replenish on Order\" dan "
"\"Beli\", purchase order akan terbuat otomatis dari sales order atau "
"manufacturing order. Setelah mengonfirmasi sales order atau manufacturing "
"order, tombol cerdas akan muncul untuk mengarahkan Anda ke <b>Permintaan "
"Penawaran (RFQ)</b>. Anda dapat melakukan perubahan yang diperlukan sebelum "
"mengonfirmasinya."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid "If the transfer is complete, you can <b>validate</b> it immediately."
msgstr ""
"Jika transfer sudah selesai, Anda dapat langsung melakukan <b>validasi</b>."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you have a partial quantity, update the quantity on the line and validate "
"it. The system will automatically create a <b>backorder</b> for the "
"remaining items."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada kuantitas parsial, perbarui kuantitas pada baris tersebut dan "
"validasi. Sistem akan otomatis membuat <b>backorder</b> untuk barang yang "
"tersisa."

#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you've configured a manufactured product with the <b>\"Replenish on "
"Order\"</b> and <b>\"Manufacturing\"</b> routes ​and a blank <b>Bill of "
"Materials (BOM)</b>, a smart button will appear on the Sales Order once it's "
"confirmed. This button will automatically redirect you to the new production "
"order, streamlining your workflow."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda telah mengonfigurasi produk manufaktur dengan rute <b>\"Replenish "
"on Order\"</b> dan rute <b>\"Produksi\"</b> serta <b>Bill of Materials (BOM)"
"</b> kosong, tombol cerdas akan muncul pada Sales Order setelah "
"dikonfirmasi. Tombol ini akan otomatis mengarahkan Anda ke order produksi "
"baru, sehingga alur kerja Anda lebih lancar."

